## Assessment Coverage

| Task | Implementation |
|------|---------------|
| Task 1 — Voice pipeline design | `llm.py` intent → RAG → SQL → verify → chart pipeline |
| Task 2 — SQL generation + prompt | `llm.py` SQL_SYSTEM prompt with 12 proven examples |
| Task 3 — KPI retrieval | `embeddings.py` ChromaDB + cosine similarity |
| Task 4 — Visualizations | `ChartView.jsx` Recharts bar/line/scatter |
| Task 5 — Reliable NL querying | Schema abstraction, KPI store, validation layers |
| Task 6 — Evaluation framework | `eval.py` 15-question benchmark with 8 metrics |